txt.en: Raiders can be found in Fushaum Bal South.\n\nYou should defeat raiders while avoiding the guards.
'Good riddance to those raiders. They died with no honour!'
A guard spotted you sneaking around!
'Mâlatuk sends raiders to try to thwart me! You must take care of this! I do not have time for these petty raiders.'
The Khundolar Commander can be found at Fushaum Bal North.\n\nYou should talk to the Khundolar Commander.
The encampment of Fushaum Bal is a lawless home to evil men once under the command of Sauron.
<rgb=#FF0000>Don't let the Fushaum Guards spot you</rgb>
